      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This specimen delivers 333 hp with the characteristic metallic rasp and instantaneous response of its individual throttle bodies. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The M-Variable differential provides exceptional lock-up for corner-exit traction. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical components\u2014including the cooling system and suspension bushings\u2014are in robust health, offering the communicative steering and balanced chassis dynamics this platform is renowned for.",
