      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! I've absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it has been incredibly reliable for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved, clean, and totally ready to hit the road with a new owner. Whether you\u2019re looking for a dependable daily commuter or something for your next road trip, this ride has plenty of life left in it! I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m excited for it to find a great new home. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
